Code preview of table Products

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('ProductWarranty') and o.name = 'FK_PRODUCTW_REFERENCE_PRODUCTS')
alter table ProductWarranty
drop constraint FK_PRODUCTW_REFERENCE_PRODUCTS
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('Products')
and type = 'U')
drop table Products
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: Products */
/*==============================================================*/
create table Products (
ProductId bigint not null,
EAN varchar(50) not null,
Sku varchar(50) not null,
Materials varchar(50) null,
Grid varchar(50) null,
CreationDate datetime not null,
Enable bit not null,
constraint PK_PRODUCTS primary key (ProductId)
)
go
